trans-unit.source: A collection of <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BufferModeSettings"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: En samling av <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BufferModeSettings"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.BufferModeSettings> object is used to define roles for event providers such as Critical, Notification, Analysis, and Logging.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Configuration.BufferModeSettings>objektet brukes til å definere roller for hendelsen leverandører som kritiske, varsling, Analysis og Logging.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.BufferModeSettings>

trans-unit.source: Each role sets buffer mode events differently.
trans-unit.target: Hver rolle angir bufferen modus hendelser annerledes.

trans-unit.source: For example, a Critical role keeps the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.BufferModeSettings.MaxBufferSize%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Configuration.BufferModeSettings.MaxFlushSize%2A> and <xref:System.Web.Configuration.BufferModeSettings.UrgentFlushInterval%2A> properties small, whereas an Analysis role sets those properties to higher values.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel en kritisk rolle beholder den <xref:System.Web.Configuration.BufferModeSettings.MaxBufferSize%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Configuration.BufferModeSettings.MaxFlushSize%2A>og <xref:System.Web.Configuration.BufferModeSettings.UrgentFlushInterval%2A>Egenskaper for liten, mens en analyse rolle angir disse egenskapene til høyere verdier.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.BufferModeSettings.UrgentFlushInterval%2A> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.BufferModeSettings.MaxFlushSize%2A> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.BufferModeSettings.MaxBufferSize%2A>

trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.BufferModesCollection"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.HealthMonitoringSection.BufferModes%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.HealthMonitoringSection> class always contains an instance of the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.BufferModesCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Configuration.HealthMonitoringSection.BufferModes%2A>Egenskapen for <xref:System.Web.Configuration.HealthMonitoringSection>klassen alltid inneholder en forekomst av <xref:System.Web.Configuration.BufferModesCollection>klassen.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.BufferModesCollection> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.HealthMonitoringSection> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.HealthMonitoringSection.BufferModes%2A>

trans-unit.source: This method inserts a `remove` element into the appropriate section of the configuration file for any element defined in a higher-level configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden setter inn en `remove` elementet i den aktuelle delen i konfigurasjonsfilen for elementer som er definert i et høyere nivå konfigurasjonsfilen.

trans-unit.target: Hvis elementet er definert i den aktuelle delen av gjeldende konfigurasjonsfilen, fjernes oppføringen i konfigurasjonsfilen.
